summary: JUST WATCHED DETECTIVE PIKACHU SPOILERS BELOW
body:
JUST WATCHED DETECTIVE PIKACHU SPOILERS BELOW

This movie is so freaking cute people!!!

  • Ryan Renolds as Pikachu did an amazing job, and he pulled off the more emotional scenes so well too
  • The CGI was so great, the moves were fantastic and the pokemon looked so cool!!!!!
  • I loved the plot and the characters, it was such a feelgood movie and i was smiling almost the entire time
  • It had the same feeling of watching an animated pokemon movie, thete were times i was at the edge of my seat, when i was close to tears, laughing at the jokes or just smiling at the adorableness
  • It wasn’t the best movie ive seen, but it was great and real caught the wonder that is pokemon ❤❤❤❤
